# Gotix Frontend

A ticketing platform frontend built with **Next.js**. This project is part of a full-stack clone that allows users to browse and book events.

## Features

- Modern UI with React & Next.js
- User authentication (sign up & log in)
- Event listings and detail pages
- Booking flow integration
- API communication with backend services

## Tech Stack

- Next.js
- React
- Tailwind CSS (or your styling choice)
- Axios
- Context API (or Redux, if used)

